1. Player is prompted for a name
2. An empty board is printed
3. Player is prompted to name a ship to place
    a. The name is checked against available ships
        i. While name is not available go back to 3
        ii. Else:
            1. Set coordinate X
                a. Check if X is inside the board
            2. Set coordinate Y
                a. Check if Y is inside the board
            3. Set direction (N, S, W, E)
                a. Check if ship places towards the given direction stays entirely inside the board
                b. Check if there are no other ships on the way
                c. Check if there are no other ships in direct proximity of the ship
        iii. If all return True add ship to ${placed_ships}
